# ===================================================================
# Revised .gitignore for Golden Algebra Project
# ===================================================================

# 1. Ignore the entire build directory
# This is still the most important rule. It handles all the clutter
# like .aux, .log, .fdb_latexmk, etc.
build/

# 2. Ignore other generated files (BUT NOT THE PDF)
# We will still ignore the SyncTeX file as it's not useful to track.
*.synctex.gz

# We are intentionally NOT ignoring *.pdf

# 3. Ignore common OS and editor junk files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~